quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  25,21,"Nnan wid ur nessarem ara timlilit yidneÂŁ: ""a lemmer id ssersen lmalayek $uĂŽne$, ne$ nwala Mass nne$""! Ni$ sme$wĂŽen aĂźas iman nnsen, u ffuhrin aĂźas."
  25,22,"Ass ideg ara walin lmalayek, ur ippili wassen d abecceĂŽ ibe$wviyen, s lxiĂŽ. A d inin: d aĂȘdid ur nepwazgar."
  25,23,"Nezzi $eĂŽ igiten nnsen, Nerra ten d a$ebbaĂŽ immebruzzĂąen."
  25,24,"Imawlan n Loennet, assen, di tnezdu$t akked trusi iufraren."
  25,25,"Ass ideg ara iceqqeq igenni s usigna, ideg ara d ssersen lmalayek, ta deffir ta,"
  25,26,"tagelda, assen, tidep, i UĂȘnin. D ass uwĂąiĂŽ i ijehliyen."
  25,27,"Ass ideg ara i$eĂ©Ă© umednus ifassen is, ad yini: ""a yamxix iw, a lemmer ddi$ d ubrid Umazan!"
  25,28,"A tawa$it pwa$e$, a lemmer ur rri$ ara winnat d aĂȘbib!"
  25,29,"Ni$ itelf iyi seg usmekti i illan iusa yi d. CciĂźan, i umdan, izga d axeddaĂą""."
  25,30,"Inna Umazan: ""a Mass iw! Ar ugdud iw, s tidep, LeqwĂŽan agi d askeĂŽfeĂ©""."
  25,31,"Akka, i yal nnbi, Nefka acengu seg ibe$wviyen. Iqadd Mass ik, i nnhaya akked usellek."
  25,32,"Nnan wid ijehlen: ""a lemmer i s d ssersen LeqwĂŽan, deg yiwet n tikelt""! Akka, iwakken a Ntebbet ul ik, yis. Nesemderri t d idurra."
